## Configuration

### Development

The app connects to `http://localhost:3000` (iOS) or `http://10.0.2.2:3000` (Android emulator) in development mode.

### Production

Update the base URL in `src/config/config.ts`:

```typescript
return 'https://api.yourapp.com';
```

